          %h2 Who we are
          %p Eclipse Design and Construction is the Houston-based architectural design and drafting firm of Miguel Alvarado. Since 2003, Eclipse's mission has been to create elegant and functional commercial and residential designs for clients at affordable pricing. Each and every project that Eclipse takes on is an opportunity to create uniqueness and beauty, thereby exceeding the expectations of the client.
          %p The cornerstone of Eclipse Design is the firm's belief in serving the client, and fulfilling all of his needs when it comes to anything related to the entire property. It is the philosophy at Eclipse Design to maintain long-term relationships with its clients, and to be of assistance even after the project is completed. 
