          %h2 Lead by example
          %p Eclipse Design and Construction understands the delicate mix between elegant architecture and function. Our team combines an in-depth understanding of manual and computer drafting procedures with techniques focusing upon functional design that are important to successful draftsmanship. We believe that architecture is a means to inspire, to unite and to create lasting art forms for generations to come. We put our passion, our spirit and our creativity into every project we touch.
