        .box-text-long
          %p Our professional, passionate and talented team has worked with a vast array of architectural creations, including educational and arts institutions, libraries, offices, residential areas, commercial and retail space, and community facilities. We draft blue prints for general contractors, and help to facilitate the process so that everything goes smoothly when it is time to build.
          %h2 Drafting
          %p Eclipse specializes in drafting procedures, both manually and electronically with techniques that concentrate on beauty and functional design that are important and essential to the success of buildings.
          %h2 Mechanical Plans
          %p Eclipse Design and its team is expertly trained in design as well as the engineering of buildings. We are experienced at designing and creating plumbing plans, electrical plans, foundation plans, structural plans, and civil engineering designs, such as drainage systems.
